{"tid":344622,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真)點解FF會叫做太空戰士?","createTime":"2017-08-02T11:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T01:13:03.000Z","uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"980efa03659c6607dd38b4aff6fdc19af148de88","tid":344622,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"關太空閪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e548d3c4a5b9de430e132023d8c654d8d556156a","tid":344622,"uid":34684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"某一代真係上太空<br />\n<br />\n然後台灣就譯做太空戰士<br />\n<br />\n(好似係)"},{"pid":"08959ca3a4a8b4e41b4767ca45d1d38664c34f5e","tid":344622,"uid":115801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/fugu.cafe/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/11235290_1655592928050229_4464730955202135853_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffugu.cafe%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F11235290_1655592928050229_4464730955202135853_o.jpg&h=56a5116b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公主蒙難記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fugu.cafe/talks/3003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffugu.cafe%2Ftalks%2F3003&d=q1ZOqM%2F6d%2B9Xcjdu9GUeKIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=1f514f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://fugu.cafe/talks/3003</a><br />\n<br />\n上太空係4代，3代我記得已叫做太空戰士。"},{"pid":"87d205841e98cd2d00718341fa0a43faef2741ca","tid":344622,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"第一隻玩就係ff8，我屌淨係得一段仔上咗太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ea956f79c87aa9384fce30d2767f3e7437c09e","tid":344622,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"出賣年齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7630fae4ad144a12383ddac0a7c31c39f1aef8f","tid":344622,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"我剛剛知乜野係FF時係睇親玩FF7,8，但覺得好悶<br />\n果時我剩係知叫太空戰士(PS1老翻)<br />\n<br />\n自己唔係死忠，模擬器爆左FF9<br />\n<br />\nNDS果幾代重制(好似係3,4？)都爆左<br />\n<br />\n比起依家果D咁靚畫質，其實比較鐘意2-3頭身Q版果D<br />\n<br />\n好記得隻FF9,不死鳥明明收伏左,但到爆機都仲未見過"},{"pid":"b1499429c5e9c78699df5e26f1e4f08e8ec27bc1","tid":344622,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:11:51.000Z","msg":"刺激1998"},{"pid":"badd802cd823ed71cc28fe981e24cb5a653ac249","tid":344622,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>刺激199<span style=\"color: red;\">5</span></blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10fe0b172381c3b9d496570d4f825ca03904b25","tid":344622,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"因為FF1 果時出左台灣中文攻略本。<br />\n你應該慶幸佢地唔係用 神鬼戰士 呢類名"},{"pid":"7bace5ff49619dd3520ad181ab3e815fecf70880","tid":344622,"uid":96983,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:06:27.000Z","msg":"台仔D譯名不嬲都9譯<br />\n格鬥天王<br />\n惡靈古堡<br />\n太空戰士<br />\n槍彈辨駁<br />\n鋼彈<br />\n潛龍諜影"},{"pid":"7204700fe79f919c4ac9cbfa0cc896498fa2f5d0","tid":344622,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台仔D譯名不嬲都9譯<br />\n格鬥天王<br />\n惡靈古堡<br />\n太空戰士<br />\n槍彈辨駁<br />\n鋼彈<br />\n潛龍諜影</blockquote><br />\n我覺得潛龍諜影個feel唔錯"},{"pid":"b754ebcd6047452857dfd0a6362a077b665ad9a4","tid":344622,"uid":122997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台仔D譯名不嬲都9譯<br />\n格鬥天王<br />\n惡靈古堡<br />\n太空戰士<br />\n槍彈辨駁<br />\n鋼彈<br />\n潛龍諜影</blockquote><br />\n我覺得潛龍諜影個feel唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而,以前有一隻game叫太保刹星,我覺得呢個名簡直神譯."},{"pid":"384486958c357b983